\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 windows
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 Of the Hilton, where he has a job in maintenance,
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 Piercing solidly through its head.  He rings the bell.
