\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 The whole seated body sticking slightly
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 As moaning howls come from his
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 Paralyzed mouth.
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 It is after having
\par \hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 Put him to bed for a nap, and then the pot,
